    "en": {
      "title": "Paddy marketing board sells ten tons of paddy in four days",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Within 4 days, the Paddy Marketing Board has purchased 1126 metric tons of paddy from the farmers, according to Mr. Neil de Alvis, Chairman of the Paddy Marketing Board.",
        "The paddy marketing board has purchased 282 metric tons of paddy only yesterday (21), which is the fourth day since it started buying paddy in the yala season.",
        "According to the Ministry of Agriculture, 73 warehouses are open for the purchase of paddy in the areas where paddy is harvested and threshed."
      ],
